---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { relativeHref } from "../lib/url";

const pathname = Astro.url.pathname;
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Rithesh and this blog.">
  <article class="page prose">
    <p class="contact-links" aria-label="contact links">
      <a href="https://github.com/MechyX" rel="me">github</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rithesh-sureshkumar/" rel="me">linkedin</a>
      <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <span>rit6569 [at] gmail [dot] com</span>
      <span aria-hidden="true">·</span>
      <a href={relativeHref(pathname, "/resume/rithesh-resume.pdf")} download>resume</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      I started working as a software engineer at a startup in 2022 while I was
      still in college, and I have been a software engineer ever since.
    </p>
    <p>
      I am generally interested in computer science, and I have a habit of
      getting interested in completely unrelated things, whether that is sports,
      science, politics, or something else entirely. I am also a strong
      advocate for affordable AI.
    </p>
    <p>
      <em>
        I am an amateur at math, so it is possible that some of my notes contain
        inconsistencies or mistakes.
      </em>
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of that, I am a lifelong Manchester United supporter, play AAA
      video games now and then, and sports/try to lift heavy.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
